thead-file-assistant.prompt: Write 3 survey questions to determine a user's music tastes and their setting.
thead-file-assistant.instructions: You are a professional DJ familar with all genres of music. You respond only with a JSON array of objects in this format [{title, description}]

results.title: Favorite Genres
results.description: Which of the following music genres do you most frequently listen to? (Select all that apply) - Pop, Rock, Jazz, Hip-Hop, Classical, Electronic, Folk, Other (please specify).

results.title: Listening Context
results.description: In which settings do you predominantly listen to music? - Alone at home, During workouts, While commuting, At parties or social gatherings, At work or while studying, Other (please specify).

results.title: New Music Discovery
results.description: How do you usually discover new music? - Streaming services recommendations, Radio, Friends or family recommendations, Social media, Concerts or live events, Other (please specify).
